Preliminary information and announcements will be published in the Official Journal of the European Union and in the procurement profile of the client.
In order to prevent discrimination against foreign interested parties, announcements at the national level must not contain additional information and must only be issued to the Office for Official Publications of the European Union once the notice has been sent.
