This employee may not be involved in the award.
The offers received must be kept under wraps until the opening date.
In the Czech Republic, the offers received are marked with a reference number.
The awarding authority records the bid data, including order numbers, as well as the production and entry data in a protocol.
Custody of the offers is not regulated in the Czech Republic.
