In the Czech Republic, a committee is conducting the opening of the bids.
Freelancers can also play a part in this.
The committee can also be tasked with other phases of the tendering process, such as the evaluation of the bids.
In Germany, a chief negotiator and a secretary are carrying out the bid opening.
